20 Creative Tattoos by the Amazing Erin Chance Tweet Posted: Sat, 3/25/2017 - 6:52am by Daniel Dominguez 
You want a realistic-yet-magical tattoo? Erin Chance is the lady to do that for you. Her work looks like myths and legends come to life. The colors are amazing, the lines are clean, and the eyes are soulful. Her work is absolutely gorgeous. Get yourself down to Virginia and get a goat woman queen tattooed on your back. 1.
